    dc:description "FIG. 6. — Itieriidae:A, Itieria cabanetiana (d’Orbigny, 1841),Lower Kimmeridgian,Oyonnax (Ain, France), paralectotype MNHN.F.A24437; B, Itieria cabanetiana, axial section,Lower Kimmeridgian,Nantua (Ain,France),MNHN.F.B11796; C, Itieria globosa Favre,1913,mould of the central cavity of the columella,Tithonian,Dörfles,Ernstbrunn,Austria,NHMW 2013/0271/0001;D, E, Peruviella dolia (Roemer,1849), Albian, Canapebe (Brazil), NHMW 2013/0050/0002; axial section, same locality, NHMW 2013/0050/0003; F, Eotrochactaeon zumoffeni (Delpey, 1939), figure from Kollmann 1982, Lower Aptian, Levadia (Greece), NHMW 1884/21/69. Scale bars: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4538507/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

